        body: "Your AskBiz account holds sensitive financial intelligence — revenue figures, profit margins, customer data, supplier relationships, cash flow, and API keys that connect to your Shopify, Amazon, and QuickBooks accounts. A compromised AskBiz account is not just an AskBiz problem: an attacker who reads your connected platform tokens could potentially access your ecommerce back-end. Treat your AskBiz account with the same rigour you would your business bank account.",
