        body: "Two-factor authentication (2FA) means that even if someone steals your password, they still cannot access your account — because they also need your phone or authenticator app to complete the login. For a business intelligence platform containing your revenue, customer, and financial data, 2FA is one of the single most important security measures you can take. We strongly recommend enabling it.",
