    title: "Value-Based Pricing: Charging What You're Worth",
    description: "How to identify what your product or service is truly worth to customers and price accordingly — without fear of losing sales.",
    topic: "Pricing & Margin Strategy",
    topicSlug: "pricing-margin-strategy",
