    title: "Amazon Buy Box: What It Is and How to Win It",
    description: "Understand the Buy Box algorithm, how to track your Buy Box win percentage, and strategies to improve it.",
    topic: "Amazon Seller Analytics",
    topicSlug: "amazon-seller-analytics",
